%% BondOrderMatrix
%%    This is the structure of the Bond Order Matrix. The elements are 
%%    in the order of the molecule they represent.
%%
%%    For each element(i.j):
%%            i .NE. j    -  0 - not bonded
%%                           1 - single bonded
%%                           2 double bonded
%%                          <0 Conjucgated (result of conjugation analysis)
%%
%%             i == j     -  0 - Normal
%%                           1 - Lone Pair
%%
%%
%%     This matrix is special type of IntSqrMat.

Structures Describing Bonding
  3 bonding
     BondOrderMatrix 41 bondordermatrix
        0 Number of Columns , Rows
          INT Size    Create
        2 Total Size of Matrix
          INT TotalSize       Create
        3 The Matrix Array
          INT Matrix Pointer Create Array=TotalSize
        DONE
DONE
